@startuml
!theme plain
title 07. Scheduler Locality and Admission
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName DejaVu Sans
left to right direction

rectangle "Workload request" as N1 #D6EAF8
rectangle "Coherence metrics" as N2 #D5F5E3
rectangle "Fabric/CXL/DPU telemetry" as N3 #FCF3CF
rectangle "Scheduler" as N4 #E8DAEF
rectangle "Placement decision" as N5 #FADBD8

N1 --> N2 : model/KV needs
N2 --> N3 : rollups
N3 --> N4 : health state
N4 --> N5 : GREEN/AMBER/RED

note bottom
Actor-facing contract: lower-layer resource identifiers remain hidden unless the ADR explicitly defines them as operator-only evidence.
end note
@enduml
